data.text:
We are called to be good stewards. How can you be a good steward?

Check out our Stewardship page and learn how you can

Take a Step in Faith

Make a difference in the lives of others, as well as your own!

Online form available: CatholicSuncook.org/stewardship

We are grateful to be able to bring FORMED to our parish community for free!

It's kind of like a Catholic Netflix! Enjoy quality Catholic programming from home, or from any device on the go! For setup instructions, please contact the office.

See our newest bulletin for the latest news and events!

Want our bulletin by email? Send your request to stjohnthebaptist@comcast.net

Know someone who's homebound and wants the bulletiin in the mail? Call 603-485-3113

We invite you to browse through our website for photo albums, our history, groups, activities, and more.

If you are visiting or new to the area, we hope to worship with you!

Let us richly live our lives of faith.

May God bless you in every season.
